# Local .terraform directories
**/.terraform/*

# .tfstate files
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*

# Crash log files
crash.log
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json

# CLI configuration files
.terraformrc
terraform.rc

# Ignore variables file containing sensitive info
terraform.tfvars
*.auto.tfvars
x.sh

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Project: GCP Infra Automation
# Purpose: Ignore local and sensitive files when working on the Terraform
#          infrastructure repository. This file was written/maintained by Aymen
#          as part of the "GCP Infra Automation" project (VPC, private Cloud
#          SQL, and secure networking via Terraform).
# Notes:
# - Keep sensitive values (for example `terraform.tfvars`) out of version
#   control. They are intentionally listed above so developers don't accidentally
#   commit secrets.
# - If you ever need to share a tfvars file safely, use a secure secret store
#   (Vault, Secret Manager) or a CI/CD secret injection approach instead.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------